know
better
than
anyone
just
what
it
takes
for
startups
to
leverage
resources
and
succeed
in
Michigan’s
autonomous
and
electrified
vehicle
technology
space.
Our
new
White
Paper
,
which
includes
case
studies
of
companies
that
are
leaders
in
innovation
—
from
autonomous
shuttles
(May
Mobility)
and
autonomous
vehicle
software,
hardware,
maps
and
cloud-support
infrastructure
(Argo
AI)
to
a
vehicle
platform
interface
(Dataspeed)
—
also
features
tips
from
Robinson
and
Pawl
for
getting
in
on
the
action
and
leveraging
resources
to
succeed.
You
can
read
about
it
all
right
here
.
